s://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAQCGNAH.png&h=2be5d4d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無啦啦乜9都未收到就想收我2萬<br />\n呢個入場費真係好hi屎貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聰明既我緊係唔會上當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我除左用字玩番條hihi轉頭<br />\n玩到佢唔再講I love you講fuck you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲嬲到block左我之外<br />\n我仲起左小小有關比關稅同超重既資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事關佢地真係整哂網頁同文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好似層層咁款<br />\n驚有寂寞的人會比呢個浪漫騙局呃到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以決定上黎公開呢一切<br />\n等大家一齊去提防受騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3eub3R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3eub3R.png&h=0a59eda8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B17Pb3S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB17Pb3S.png&h=531365e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UFDCkXd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUFDCkXd.png&h=5e001689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真人真事 完。謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffa06d7a1dd074bbecad95be3a055aa0ac52002","tid":1080532,"uid":77569,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:12:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20a45605c2156d31be599c08e4d8e1c5e32b5713","tid":1080532,"uid":231850,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cffa06d7a1dd074bbecad95be3a055aa0ac52002","tid":1080532,"uid":77569,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:12:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:14